                <note rend="inline" type="source">611.125/75: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Mexico</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Sheffield</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1926-07-24T12:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 24, 1926—noon</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>244. Your 321, July 23, 2 p.m.<note n="25" xml:id="d246fn25">Not printed.</note>
                    Your despatch 2532 has just been received.<note n="25" xml:id="d246fn26">Not
                        printed.</note> It will be entirely agreeable to this Government to <pb
                        facs="0421" n="311" xml:id="pg_311"/> hold conference in Washington instead
                    of El Paso. Please so advise Foreign Office.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
